%TUTORIAL ------------------------- BROWSE ----------------------------
%OPTION  ===>_ZCMD
%
%                     -----------------------------------
                      ×             BROWSE              ×
                      -----------------------------------

  %Browse+allows you to display data contained within a selected library
   full screen format.

   You can scroll the data in two directions (up or down) by a half page
   full page, or by any number of lines.  Scrolling is performed by mean
   the scroll commands.

   The top right hand corner of the browse screen will supply the select
   library name and sort sequence if sorted.

   Once a manual is located it can be selected by entering a 'S' in fron
   the Manual ID field.  Detail information will then be displayed for t
   selected manual.

                            (Continued on next page)

)INIT
   &ZCONT = SLSS1001
   &ZUP   = SLSST000
)END
